  <VideoGallery videoIds={['rio-turquesa-cascada','rio-turquesa-rocas']} lang="en" title="Thermal river videos" columns={2} />

  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="faq-t">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header"><h2 id="faq-t">Questions about the river</h2></div>
      <div class="faq-list"><details><summary>Can you swim in the Tolantongo River?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes, the river is navigable and swimmable throughout its entire course. The depth varies but most of the route allows for comfortable walking or swimming.</div></details><details><summary>Is there a dangerous current in the river?</summary><div class="faq-answer">The current is gentle for most of the route. During the rainy season it may increase. Always respect the destination's signage about accessible areas.</div></details><details><summary>Is river access included with admission?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Walking the river route is part of the general access to the destination. There is no additional cost.</div></details></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
